---
import Button from "./Button.astro";
---

<section class="faq-section">
  <h2>FAQ</h2>
  <div class="faq-items">
    <div class="faq-item faq-item1">
      <h3>What are the opening hours and address?</h3>
      <p>
        - Thursday 18.00-01.00, Friday 18.00-04.00 and Saturday: 18.00-03.00.
        Music will play all the hours. Address is Refshalevej 193, 1432
        Copenhagen.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item faq-item2">
      <h3>Can I join the festival with mobility impairment?</h3>
      <p>
        - Yes, but you need to bring a companion (free of charge if documented)
        and be prepared for a rough ride. Most of the surface is grass or wood
        chips and it can be muddy. Unfortunately there will not be
        raised viewing spots for mobility impairment.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item faq-item3">
      <h3>How do I exchange my PDF ticket?</h3>
      <p>
        - Go to the ticket office located on the way to the entrance. You can
        pick up your wristband from 17.00.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item faq-item4">
      <h3>What will there be on site?</h3>
      <p>
        - 3 music stages, a vintage carousel ride, nice bars and food stands,
        the witch cave, performances, bonfire, power banks, free water point,
        merchandise and info stand and much more.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="button-container">
    <Button buttontext="More FAQ’s here" />
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .faq-section {
    padding: 20px;
    background-image: url("../imgs/faqimg.webp");
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    fill-opacity: #6d2bc44f;
  }

  /* Mobile-first: Display elements in a column for small screens */
  .faq-items {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .faq-item {
    background-color: var(--primary);
    padding: 15px;
    margin: 10px;
    transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .faq-item:hover {
    background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1);
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  /* Stil for h2 i sektionen */
  .faq-section h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .faq-section h3,
  .faq-section p {
    color: var(--quaternary);
  }

  .button-container {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-top: 20px;
  }

  /* Tablet and larger: Create grid layout for larger screens */
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .faq-items {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(12, 1fr); /* 12 kolonner */
      grid-template-rows: repeat(6, auto); /* Flere rækker */
      gap: 30px;
    }

    /* Placering af elementerne i grid for at opnå asymmetrisk layout */
    .faq-item1 {
      grid-column: 1 / span 5;
      grid-row: 1 / span 2;
    }

    .faq-item2 {
      grid-column: 6 / span 7;
      grid-row: 1 / span 3;
    }

    .faq-item3 {
      grid-column: 1 / span 6;
      grid-row: 3 / span 3;
    }

    .faq-item4 {
      grid-column: 7 / span 6;
      grid-row: 4 / span 2;
    }
  }
</style>

